reviewText: My son has a wrestling heart from his high school years.  This was just a nice way for him to enjoy some good wrestling.
I bought it to see the young Christine Sinclair and I'm not disappointed. I love it.
thanks for offering this on DVD!

Great to go back and watch the entire Sanderson family support Cael as he goes for his 4th title and undefeated college career.  Fun for me to go back and watch the other wrestlers who were wrestling at the time.
